Creating KPIs 13

Creating OpenRate KPI

- In Visualizations click to KPI

- Drag and drop OpenRate Measure to Indicator

- Drag and drop SortDate column to Trend axis

- Drag and drop PreMOpenRate to Target goals


Creating BounceRate KPI

- In Visualizations click to KPI

- Drag and drop BounceRate Measure to Indicator

- Drag and drop SortDate column to Trend axis

- Drag and drop PreMBounceRate to Target goals


Change the color coding for BounceRate KPI to “Low is good” because our target is to get the BounceRate lower.

- (1) Click BounceRate KPI ---> (2) Click to Format ---> (3) Color coding ---> (4) Change the Direction to “Low is good”


Creating Recipients KPI

- In Visualizations click to KPI

- Drag and drop Recipients Measure to Indicator

- Drag and drop SortDate column to Trend axis

- Drag and drop Recipients to Target goals


Creating TotalEmail KPI

- In Visualizations click to KPI

- Drag and drop TotalEmail Measure to Indicator

- Drag and drop SortDate column to Trend axis

- Drag and drop TotalEmail to Target goals


Fixing the visualization of the KPIs

- (1) Click to the KPI

- (2) Click to Format

- (3) Click to Title ---> Turn On

- (4) Change Title to OpenRate / BounceRate / Recipients / Total Email

- (5) Change the Font color to “White” and the Background color to “Green”

- (6) Choose the middle Alignment

- (7) Change the Text size to “11”

- (8) Turn on the Border

- (9) Change the color to green

- (10) Change the size of the  KPI by dragging the KPI
